A DNS RR for specifying the location of
services (DNS SRV)
2000", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC2782.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document describes a DNS RR which specifies the location of the server(s) for a specific protocol and domain. [STANDARDS-TRACK]"];
  cites -> RFC2782;
  RFC4651 [label="RFC4651
A Taxonomy and Analysis of Enhancements
to Mobile IPv6 Route Optimization
2007", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC4651.html", target="_top", tooltip="This document describes and evaluates strategies to enhance Mobile IPv6 Route Optimization, on the basis of existing proposals, in order to motivate and guide further research in this context.  This document is a product of the IP Mobility Optimizations (MobOpts) Research Group.  This memo provides information for the Internet community."];
